      <div class="ui raised segment">
        <h2 class="ui large header">Articles on humor:</h2>
        <ul class="ui list">
          <li class="item text"><a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19653782" target="_blank">Finding comfort in a joke: consolatory effects of humor through cognitive distraction.</a></li>
